title: Jennifer Aniston surprised unsuspecting 'Friends' fans
description: While hosting "The Ellen DeGeneres Show," Jennifer Aniston surprised "Friends" fans on the Central Perk set and talked to Will Ferrell about his most enduring role as Buddy the Elf.

title: The WHO should sound the alarm on Wuhan coronavirus
description: As the Wuhan coronavirus continues to spread around the world, the World Health Organization's decision to hold off on declaring the outbreak "a public health emergency of international concern" is baffling.

title: Republic Day 2020: Join India's great big constitution party
description: India is the world's largest democracy, and it's serious about its constitution. The country goes all out to celebrate its remarkable achievement in self-governing each Republic Day.

title: Death toll rises as healthcare workers say supplies are running out
description: The death toll from the Wuhan coronavirus in China continues rising as authorities and health care workers struggle to contain the outbreak.

title: Man charged with human trafficking after police allege he kept sex slave for 5 years
description: A North Carolina man is facing a human trafficking charge after police alleged he kept a person in sexual servitude for five years.

title: Louise Linton sides with Greta Thunberg after husband Steve Mnuchin takes jab at activist
description: Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin's wife Louise Linton on Saturday showed support for climate activist Greta Thunberg, days after her husband took a jab at the teenager.
